WEBVTT

00:00:11.230 --> 00:00:13.400 line:80%
[Sui]

00:00:13.490 --> 00:00:15.720 line:80%
[Xie]

00:00:14.520 --> 00:00:15.800 line:80%
Soldiers!

00:00:16.630 --> 00:00:19.440 line:80%
Kill Lord Changxin with no mercy!

00:00:19.600 --> 00:00:20.960 line:80%
Charge!

00:00:20.960 --> 00:00:22.240 line:80%
Hyah! Hyah!

00:00:22.240 --> 00:00:23.830 line:80%
Charge!

00:00:23.990 --> 00:00:28.830 line:80%
Charge!

00:00:40.950 --> 00:00:44.270 line:80%
Charge!

00:00:41.550 --> 00:00:42.480 line:80%
[He]

00:00:55.270 --> 00:00:56.120 line:80%
Lord Li!

00:01:12.720 --> 00:01:13.870 line:80%
Soldiers!

00:01:16.510 --> 00:01:18.870 line:80%
Lord Changxin's main force
has started attacking the city!

00:01:18.870 --> 00:01:20.280 line:80%
Follow me

00:01:20.670 --> 00:01:22.470 line:80%
to the rear of the Chongzhou Army

00:01:22.720 --> 00:01:24.110 line:80%
and go straight to Lord Changxin!

00:01:24.110 --> 00:01:25.000 line:80%
Yes!

00:01:25.080 --> 00:01:26.750 line:80%
Lord Li, you're badly injured.

00:01:26.750 --> 00:01:28.210 line:80%
Don't fight them head-on.

00:01:28.310 --> 00:01:29.360 line:80%
Leave it to us.

00:01:29.360 --> 00:01:30.360 line:80%
We will handle it!

00:01:33.660 --> 00:01:35.640 line:80%
If my life can save more people,

00:01:37.110 --> 00:01:38.770 line:80%
then my death will be worth it.

00:01:44.070 --> 00:01:44.529 line:80%
Mr. Jin.

00:01:47.690 --> 00:01:48.089 line:80%
You...

00:01:48.839 --> 00:01:49.300 line:80%
My Lord!

00:01:51.720 --> 00:01:52.320 line:80%
Lord Zhuo,

00:01:52.930 --> 00:01:54.460 line:80%
take Lord Li to a safe place

00:01:54.480 --> 00:01:55.360 line:80%
and take good care of him.

00:01:55.360 --> 00:01:57.000 line:80%
As for destroying the rebels' stronghold,

00:01:57.000 --> 00:01:58.000 line:80%
we will handle it.

00:01:59.470 --> 00:02:01.160 line:80%
Mrs. Fan, we'll go with you!

00:02:01.850 --> 00:02:02.430 line:80%
We'll go with you!

00:02:02.430 --> 00:02:04.030 line:80%
-We'll go with you!
-We'll go with you, Mrs. Fan!

00:02:04.030 --> 00:02:05.970 line:80%
-We'll go with you!
-We'll go with you!

00:02:05.970 --> 00:02:06.970 line:80%
We'll go with you!

00:03:36.740 --> 00:03:41.770 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:03:41.870 --> 00:03:44.450 line:80%
[Episode 30]

00:04:04.250 --> 00:04:06.840 line:80%
♪ There's an unknown storm ahead ♪

00:04:07.210 --> 00:04:08.960 line:80%
♪ After a long night ♪

00:04:09.970 --> 00:04:12.320 line:80%
♪ Only then did I see the light of dawn ♪

00:04:12.980 --> 00:04:14.870 line:80%
♪ The stubbornness in my palms ♪

00:04:15.510 --> 00:04:18.280 line:80%
♪ Walk a rugged path
with honesty and integrity ♪

00:04:18.910 --> 00:04:22.830 line:80%
♪ Trampling along the way. In the end ♪

00:04:23.420 --> 00:04:26.600 line:80%
♪ It will all be worth it ♪

00:04:27.360 --> 00:04:29.240 line:80%
♪ Fate, on its unstoppable path ♪

00:04:29.890 --> 00:04:32.170 line:80%
♪ Burns away sorrow
and lays the seeds of kindness ♪

00:04:32.760 --> 00:04:33.709 line:80%
♪ The starlight in the dark ♪

00:04:34.240 --> 00:04:38.350 line:80%
♪ Will eventually light the way
for the heart ♪

00:04:39.230 --> 00:04:41.360 line:80%
♪ Fate, on its galloping path ♪

00:04:41.940 --> 00:04:44.270 line:80%
♪ Sheds all hesitation
and tempers its edge ♪

00:04:44.840 --> 00:04:45.690 line:80%
♪ The desire hidden in your eyes ♪

00:04:46.330 --> 00:04:50.400 line:80%
♪ Will one day spark the fire of love ♪

00:04:51.260 --> 00:04:53.320 line:80%
♪ The gaze of the world is light ♪

00:04:51.270 --> 00:04:52.220 line:80%
[He]

00:04:52.720 --> 00:04:54.630 line:80%
Why is He Jingyuan's army here?

00:04:53.959 --> 00:04:56.459 line:80%
♪ With hearts united,
the weak can defeat the strong ♪

00:04:55.959 --> 00:04:57.870 line:80%
Stop them!
Don't let them disrupt our formation!

00:04:57.150 --> 00:04:59.280 line:80%
♪ The world is full of ups and downs ♪

00:04:57.890 --> 00:04:58.930 line:80%
Yes! Follow me!

00:04:59.110 --> 00:04:59.870 line:80%
Hyah!

00:04:59.890 --> 00:05:00.190 line:80%
Hyah!

00:04:59.970 --> 00:05:04.280 line:80%
♪ Kindness can only belong
to the victorious ♪

00:05:02.160 --> 00:05:02.800 line:80%
Hyah!

00:05:02.990 --> 00:05:03.600 line:80%
Hyah!

00:05:15.480 --> 00:05:16.070 line:80%
Hyah!

00:05:16.550 --> 00:05:17.800 line:80%
Report from the front line!

00:05:17.800 --> 00:05:19.230 line:80%
We have breached the city walls,

00:05:19.230 --> 00:05:21.030 line:80%
but casualties are heavy.
We need reinforcements immediately!

00:05:21.030 --> 00:05:22.840 line:80%
Very well. Go there at once.

00:05:44.500 --> 00:05:47.070 line:80%
[He]

00:05:52.709 --> 00:05:53.500 line:80%
Yan Zheng!

00:06:04.670 --> 00:06:05.840 line:80%
I knew you would come.

00:06:05.840 --> 00:06:07.370 line:80%
Stay behind me. Keep close.

00:06:11.990 --> 00:06:13.520 line:80%
I won't hide behind anyone.

00:06:14.670 --> 00:06:16.960 line:80%
Lord Changxin or Sui Yuanqing? Pick one.

00:06:21.920 --> 00:06:22.800 line:80%
Lord Changxin.

00:06:22.820 --> 00:06:23.700 line:80%
Be careful.

00:06:28.600 --> 00:06:29.190 line:80%
Hyah!

00:06:48.820 --> 00:06:50.230 line:80%
[He]

00:07:10.260 --> 00:07:10.750 line:80%
[Sui]

00:07:33.630 --> 00:07:34.360 line:80%
Brother!

00:07:48.400 --> 00:07:50.260 line:80%
Then you can die with him!

00:07:58.510 --> 00:08:00.270 line:80%
Mandi!

00:08:02.230 --> 00:08:04.440 line:80%
Sui Yuanqing! I'll kill you!

00:08:09.990 --> 00:08:10.670 line:80%
Brother!

00:08:10.690 --> 00:08:11.330 line:80%
Mandi!

00:08:11.520 --> 00:08:12.310 line:80%
Mandi!

00:08:12.830 --> 00:08:13.740 line:80%
Mandi!

00:08:14.310 --> 00:08:15.240 line:80%
-Mandi!
-Mandi!

00:08:15.280 --> 00:08:16.170 line:80%
Mandi!

00:08:16.430 --> 00:08:17.250 line:80%
Mandi!

00:08:18.360 --> 00:08:19.040 line:80%
Yuanqing!

00:08:19.630 --> 00:08:21.830 line:80%
Lead the troops to attack the city, now!

00:08:23.920 --> 00:08:24.600 line:80%
Mandi!

00:08:25.230 --> 00:08:25.920 line:80%
Mandi!

00:08:30.500 --> 00:08:31.220 line:80%
Mandi!

00:08:32.589 --> 00:08:33.310 line:80%
Mandi!

00:08:33.469 --> 00:08:34.310 line:80%
Mandi!

00:08:34.849 --> 00:08:35.790 line:80%
Mandi!

00:08:36.640 --> 00:08:38.800 line:80%
Mandi!

00:08:39.040 --> 00:08:40.950 line:80%
Mandi!

00:08:41.719 --> 00:08:42.790 line:80%
Xie brat!

00:08:43.349 --> 00:08:45.080 line:80%
Do you really think you can win?

00:08:45.240 --> 00:08:47.240 line:80%
Look at the smoke signals behind me.

00:08:47.640 --> 00:08:50.680 line:80%
The Chongzhou Army
has already breached Lucheng!

00:08:51.240 --> 00:08:53.950 line:80%
You can't go anywhere today!

00:08:56.040 --> 00:08:57.130 line:80%
Xie Wu!

00:08:58.070 --> 00:08:59.350 line:80%
Stay here and protect Changyu!

00:08:59.350 --> 00:08:59.920 line:80%
Yes!

00:09:00.750 --> 00:09:01.400 line:80%
Hyah!

00:09:02.430 --> 00:09:04.470 line:80%
Where are you running, Xie brat?

00:09:04.840 --> 00:09:05.390 line:80%
Hyah!

00:09:07.710 --> 00:09:08.280 line:80%
Hyah!

00:09:18.440 --> 00:09:19.880 line:80%
How strange.

00:09:20.300 --> 00:09:22.180 line:80%
How dare a pawn like you stop me?

00:09:22.200 --> 00:09:24.260 line:80%
To kill a rebellious old man like you,

00:09:24.400 --> 00:09:25.550 line:80%
I can do it alone!

00:09:25.880 --> 00:09:27.290 line:80%
Arrogant brat.

00:09:27.310 --> 00:09:29.640 line:80%
When I was leading armies to kill enemies,

00:09:30.110 --> 00:09:31.700 line:80%
you were still a kid.

00:09:47.760 --> 00:09:48.660 line:80%
Not bad, kid.

00:09:48.710 --> 00:09:51.440 line:80%
Following that Xie brat
is a waste of your talent.

00:09:51.670 --> 00:09:53.270 line:80%
Why not follow me from now on?

00:09:55.160 --> 00:09:56.760 line:80%
I am a Xie for life.

00:09:57.160 --> 00:09:58.280 line:80%
I will never take a dog's last name!

00:09:58.280 --> 00:10:00.210 line:80%
You don't know what's good for you.

00:10:11.640 --> 00:10:12.800 line:80%
You're good with short blades,

00:10:12.800 --> 00:10:14.240 line:80%
but your moves are heavy and powerful.

00:10:14.240 --> 00:10:15.430 line:80%
Use less brute force,

00:10:15.430 --> 00:10:16.310 line:80%
go with the flow,

00:10:16.310 --> 00:10:17.440 line:80%
and use more finesse

00:10:41.260 --> 00:10:42.500 line:80%
On the battlefield,

00:10:42.550 --> 00:10:45.350 line:80%
the enemy's moves change in an instant.

00:10:47.090 --> 00:10:49.180 line:80%
How can you lose your composure

00:10:49.430 --> 00:10:51.830 line:80%
the moment someone sees through your move?

00:11:21.470 --> 00:11:24.330 line:80%
You think you can defeat me
with these petty tricks?

00:11:25.450 --> 00:11:26.630 line:80%
Kill me.

00:11:28.430 --> 00:11:29.780 line:80%
Make it quick!

00:11:32.120 --> 00:11:33.920 line:80%
Tie him up. Take him back.

00:11:34.080 --> 00:11:34.590 line:80%
Yes!

00:11:43.030 --> 00:11:46.830 line:80%
♪ The world is vast ♪

00:11:48.350 --> 00:11:54.450 line:80%
♪ The storm is rising ♪

00:11:48.830 --> 00:11:50.510 line:80%
Who is He Jingyuan to you?

00:11:51.130 --> 00:11:53.390 line:80%
He is the commander of our Jizhou Army.

00:11:55.160 --> 00:11:56.630 line:80%
This blade technique of yours

00:11:56.010 --> 00:12:00.250 line:80%
♪ Day and night ♪

00:11:57.120 --> 00:11:59.430 line:80%
was created by
the Two Tiger Generals of the Wei Family.

00:11:59.430 --> 00:12:01.210 line:80%
But Wei Qilin is dead.

00:12:01.360 --> 00:12:05.080 line:80%
♪ We strive to save the world ♪

00:12:01.470 --> 00:12:03.830 line:80%
Only He Jingyuan
still knows this technique.

00:12:03.830 --> 00:12:05.880 line:80%
How did you learn it from him?

00:12:06.240 --> 00:12:08.450 line:80%
You know General He's sworn brother?

00:12:08.640 --> 00:12:10.590 line:80%
The big traitor Wei Qilin?

00:12:08.930 --> 00:12:13.370 line:80%
♪ All people ♪

00:12:10.640 --> 00:12:11.710 line:80%
Who doesn't know him?

00:12:11.710 --> 00:12:13.120 line:80%
Who hasn't heard of him?

00:12:14.570 --> 00:12:19.980 line:80%
♪ Are part of the past ♪

00:12:22.230 --> 00:12:27.010 line:80%
♪ What's the date today? ♪

00:12:26.990 --> 00:12:28.520 line:80%
Once I have captured you,

00:12:27.530 --> 00:12:35.080 line:80%
♪ How lamentable ♪

00:12:28.640 --> 00:12:30.550 line:80%
while He Jingyuan is still barely alive,

00:12:30.550 --> 00:12:32.680 line:80%
I'll negotiate another deal with him!

00:12:45.260 --> 00:12:49.040 line:80%
♪ The world is vast ♪

00:12:50.650 --> 00:12:56.720 line:80%
♪ The storm is rising ♪

00:12:58.240 --> 00:13:02.530 line:80%
♪ Day and night ♪

00:13:03.690 --> 00:13:07.410 line:80%
♪ We strive to save the world ♪

00:13:10.130 --> 00:13:13.270 line:80%
Please send troops
to rescue them immediately!

00:13:11.310 --> 00:13:15.670 line:80%
♪ All people ♪

00:13:16.800 --> 00:13:22.280 line:80%
♪ Are part of the past ♪

00:13:24.460 --> 00:13:29.100 line:80%
♪ What's the date today? ♪

00:13:29.760 --> 00:13:37.530 line:80%
♪ How lamentable ♪

00:13:38.220 --> 00:13:40.640 line:80%
[Sui]

00:13:43.240 --> 00:13:47.590 line:80%
[Jizhou Government Office]

00:13:53.710 --> 00:13:55.240 line:80%
How did a fine young lady...

00:13:56.190 --> 00:13:57.470 line:80%
get hurt like this?

00:14:06.310 --> 00:14:08.170 line:80%
I didn't mean to hide my identity.

00:14:10.150 --> 00:14:11.240 line:80%
Are you...

00:14:12.310 --> 00:14:13.280 line:80%
angry?

00:14:19.050 --> 00:14:20.510 line:80%
Back in the military camp,

00:14:20.640 --> 00:14:22.550 line:80%
I knew you were not just anybody.

00:14:23.430 --> 00:14:24.800 line:80%
But I never expected

00:14:25.240 --> 00:14:27.440 line:80%
that you were the noble Princess Royal.

00:14:29.710 --> 00:14:31.640 line:80%
And now you're treating my injury.

00:14:33.880 --> 00:14:36.470 line:80%
I also thought my status was noble,

00:14:37.120 --> 00:14:39.550 line:80%
and that agreeing to a marriage alliance
for the country

00:14:39.550 --> 00:14:41.950 line:80%
would be the greatest sacrifice
of my life.

00:14:42.640 --> 00:14:45.240 line:80%
But after going to the battlefield,
I realized

00:14:45.550 --> 00:14:47.680 line:80%
being a Princess Royal means nothing.

00:14:51.500 --> 00:14:53.300 line:80%
Now, beheading the rebel leader

00:14:53.760 --> 00:14:55.950 line:80%
is a glory you earned with your own hands.

00:14:55.950 --> 00:14:57.680 line:80%
Now that Lord Changxin is dead,

00:14:57.920 --> 00:15:00.120 line:80%
the court and the public will be shaken.

00:15:00.120 --> 00:15:03.050 line:80%
Your name will be remembered
by everyone in Great Yin

00:15:03.120 --> 00:15:04.520 line:80%
and recorded in history.

00:15:14.550 --> 00:15:15.480 line:80%
I'm bowing to you

00:15:16.550 --> 00:15:17.810 line:80%
as the Princess Royal,

00:15:19.050 --> 00:15:20.280 line:80%
and also as Qi Shu.

00:15:22.580 --> 00:15:24.580 line:80%
Changyu, have a good rest.

00:15:29.800 --> 00:15:30.830 line:80%
I used to think...

00:15:32.190 --> 00:15:33.590 line:80%
that as long as I was kind,

00:15:35.620 --> 00:15:37.550 line:80%
I could protect those around me.

00:15:42.190 --> 00:15:45.920 line:80%
But after experiencing
life and death separations, I realized...

00:15:46.930 --> 00:15:48.160 line:80%
misplaced kindness

00:15:48.370 --> 00:15:50.980 line:80%
will only drive more people
to desperation.

00:15:51.240 --> 00:15:52.000 line:80%
Sister...

00:15:52.470 --> 00:15:53.070 line:80%
I'm here.

00:15:53.400 --> 00:15:54.260 line:80%
I'm right here.

00:15:54.430 --> 00:15:54.960 line:80%
I'm here.

00:15:55.000 --> 00:15:55.660 line:80%
Brother...

00:15:55.670 --> 00:15:56.200 line:80%
I'm here.

00:15:57.800 --> 00:15:59.370 line:80%
Look how well I've done.

00:15:59.590 --> 00:16:02.240 line:80%
I... I'm not a coward.

00:16:08.830 --> 00:16:09.760 line:80%
Mandi!

00:16:09.830 --> 00:16:12.170 line:80%
Mandi!

00:16:14.870 --> 00:16:16.350 line:80%
Godfather was right.

00:16:17.980 --> 00:16:19.310 line:80%
On the battlefield,

00:16:20.200 --> 00:16:22.530 line:80%
it's either you die or your opponent does.

00:16:22.670 --> 00:16:23.620 line:80%
Where is General He?

00:16:23.620 --> 00:16:26.030 line:80%
General He... is on the city walls.

00:16:26.160 --> 00:16:26.830 line:80%
Hurry!

00:16:40.160 --> 00:16:42.040 line:80%
General, we won!

00:16:41.150 --> 00:16:42.550 line:80%
[He]

00:16:44.590 --> 00:16:45.340 line:80%
General?

00:16:51.520 --> 00:16:52.280 line:80%
General?

00:16:58.550 --> 00:16:59.510 line:80%
General?

00:17:05.590 --> 00:17:07.159 line:80%
General!

00:17:08.389 --> 00:17:10.340 line:80%
General!

00:17:11.530 --> 00:17:13.129 line:80%
If I had known this...

00:17:14.440 --> 00:17:16.590 line:80%
if I had killed Lord Changxin sooner,

00:17:19.260 --> 00:17:21.659 line:80%
General He and the others wouldn't have...

00:17:25.310 --> 00:17:26.899 line:80%
General He's death

00:17:28.070 --> 00:17:29.150 line:80%
is not your fault.

00:17:35.000 --> 00:17:35.870 line:80%
Changyu,

00:17:37.470 --> 00:17:38.860 line:80%
he was just like you—

00:17:42.280 --> 00:17:44.390 line:80%
wanting to protect this land.

00:17:45.350 --> 00:17:48.550 line:80%
Your Highness, Mrs. Fan,
Lord Li is requesting a meeting.

00:17:53.590 --> 00:17:54.480 line:80%
Let him in.

00:17:55.150 --> 00:17:55.870 line:80%
Changyu,

00:17:57.280 --> 00:17:58.350 line:80%
take a good rest.

00:17:59.240 --> 00:18:00.040 line:80%
I'm off now.

00:18:09.680 --> 00:18:10.400 line:80%
Captain Li.

00:18:12.240 --> 00:18:13.700 line:80%
You all have earned merit.

00:18:15.520 --> 00:18:16.390 line:80%
Recover well.

00:18:38.030 --> 00:18:38.830 line:80%
Lord Li.

00:18:39.210 --> 00:18:41.210 line:80%
Commandant Fan, you played the hero

00:18:42.240 --> 00:18:44.040 line:80%
and finally got what you wanted.

00:18:47.800 --> 00:18:49.350 line:80%
You were injured too badly.

00:18:50.960 --> 00:18:51.910 line:80%
Knocking you out

00:18:53.150 --> 00:18:54.960 line:80%
was to stop you from acting rashly

00:18:54.960 --> 00:18:56.640 line:80%
and throwing your life away.

00:18:57.110 --> 00:18:59.590 line:80%
I would rather have died outside the city

00:19:00.720 --> 00:19:02.880 line:80%
than be knocked out,

00:19:02.960 --> 00:19:05.550 line:80%
only to wake up
and be told the battle is over.

00:19:07.760 --> 00:19:09.290 line:80%
It's even impossible for me

00:19:09.800 --> 00:19:10.950 line:80%
to avenge my master.

00:19:12.550 --> 00:19:14.150 line:80%
I'm just a joke now.

00:19:15.350 --> 00:19:17.440 line:80%
It would be a real joke

00:19:18.350 --> 00:19:21.150 line:80%
if Lord He's prized disciple
were to die foolishly

00:19:21.870 --> 00:19:23.310 line:80%
in a moment of anger.

00:19:37.280 --> 00:19:38.480 line:80%
I came here

00:19:41.070 --> 00:19:42.870 line:80%
to fulfill Master's dying wish.

00:19:47.940 --> 00:19:49.180 line:80%
[To He]

00:19:49.960 --> 00:19:51.800 line:80%
Let's not meet again.

00:20:18.420 --> 00:20:20.770 line:80%
[To He]

00:20:27.520 --> 00:20:28.840 line:80%
He...

00:20:28.600 --> 00:20:30.410 line:80%
[Thanks to your help, He,]

00:20:29.110 --> 00:20:29.960 line:80%
Help...

00:20:33.310 --> 00:20:35.770 line:80%
In shame... 100,000...

00:20:33.480 --> 00:20:35.980 line:80%
[Now the Prime Minister
has issued another kill order.]

00:20:35.960 --> 00:20:38.290 line:80%
Thanks to your help, He,

00:20:38.520 --> 00:20:40.660 line:80%
I have lived until now in shame.

00:20:41.630 --> 00:20:46.450 line:80%
I wish to restore the truth
to the 100,000 souls of Jinzhou.

00:20:47.030 --> 00:20:50.030 line:80%
Now the Prime Minister
has issued another kill order.

00:20:52.280 --> 00:20:54.550 line:80%
Blabla... can no longer live in shame.

00:20:55.140 --> 00:20:58.580 line:80%
Nor do I wish to put you
in a difficult position.

00:21:00.760 --> 00:21:02.990 line:80%
I, Qilin, can no longer live in shame.

00:21:03.800 --> 00:21:06.400 line:80%
Nor do I wish to put you
in a difficult position.

00:21:06.480 --> 00:21:08.650 line:80%
I will end my life along with my wife.

00:21:07.890 --> 00:21:10.090 line:80%
[I, Qilin, can no longer live in shame.]

00:21:10.310 --> 00:21:11.590 line:80%
Our lives

00:21:11.590 --> 00:21:13.320 line:80%
have lasted 16 extra years.

00:21:13.780 --> 00:21:18.660 line:80%
[I, Qilin, can no longer live in shame.]

00:21:14.550 --> 00:21:16.240 line:80%
It has been a great fortune.

00:21:16.260 --> 00:21:17.730 line:80%
I beg you, He,

00:21:17.870 --> 00:21:19.670 line:80%
to protect

00:21:20.520 --> 00:21:22.070 line:80%
my two daughters.

00:21:23.480 --> 00:21:24.110 line:80%
Sister.

00:21:25.770 --> 00:21:26.680 line:80%
Sister?

00:21:29.440 --> 00:21:30.150 line:80%
Coward,

00:21:30.590 --> 00:21:33.150 line:80%
pretend you never saw this letter today.

00:21:33.480 --> 00:21:35.610 line:80%
And don't tell anyone else about this.

00:21:37.680 --> 00:21:39.830 line:80%
Leave the letter here. Go back now.

00:21:40.550 --> 00:21:41.550 line:80%
Alright, Sister.

00:21:49.440 --> 00:21:51.500 line:80%
You know General He's sworn brother?

00:21:52.070 --> 00:21:54.110 line:80%
The big traitor Wei Qilin?

00:21:54.110 --> 00:21:55.200 line:80%
Who doesn't know him?

00:21:55.200 --> 00:21:56.530 line:80%
Who hasn't heard of him?

00:21:58.580 --> 00:22:02.870 line:80%
The big traitor, Wei Qilin.

00:22:03.120 --> 00:22:06.810 line:80%
He escorted the grain with no loyalty

00:22:03.560 --> 00:22:09.450 line:80%
[Wei Qilin]

00:22:07.550 --> 00:22:11.520 line:80%
and cost 100,000 heroes their lives!

00:22:11.590 --> 00:22:12.720 line:80%
My father was Wei...

00:22:15.280 --> 00:22:16.390 line:80%
Wei Qilin?

00:22:17.280 --> 00:22:18.760 line:80%
The big traitor Wei Qilin?

00:22:19.160 --> 00:22:20.220 line:80%
That can't be true.

00:22:21.150 --> 00:22:22.150 line:80%
That can't be true. That can't be true.

00:22:22.150 --> 00:22:24.930 line:80%
If my father were a traitor
who harmed the country and the people,

00:22:24.930 --> 00:22:26.330 line:80%
with my mother's temper,

00:22:26.800 --> 00:22:28.530 line:80%
how could she ever forgive him?

00:22:30.480 --> 00:22:32.630 line:80%
But what exactly happened?

00:22:34.650 --> 00:22:39.540 line:80%
Crown Prince Chengde
and General Xie Linshan

00:22:39.630 --> 00:22:41.720 line:80%
defended the border,

00:22:41.720 --> 00:22:44.000 line:80%
fighting valiantly on the battlefield.

00:22:44.000 --> 00:22:47.480 line:80%
The big traitor Wei Qilin
colluded with Beijue,

00:22:47.480 --> 00:22:49.640 line:80%
delaying the army's provisions.

00:22:49.800 --> 00:22:51.060 line:80%
One hundred thousand soldiers

00:22:51.060 --> 00:22:55.060 line:80%
starved for 5 days and nights.

00:22:55.480 --> 00:22:57.530 line:80%
The big traitor Wei Qilin.

00:22:57.620 --> 00:22:59.550 line:80%
Who doesn't know him?

00:22:59.210 --> 00:23:01.850 line:80%
[Wei Qilin]

00:22:59.550 --> 00:23:01.910 line:80%
Who hasn't heard of him?

00:23:01.930 --> 00:23:06.130 line:80%
The big traitor, Wei Qilin.

00:23:04.710 --> 00:23:05.440 line:80%
[Wei Qilin]

00:23:06.430 --> 00:23:10.680 line:80%
He escorted the grain with no loyalty

00:23:07.510 --> 00:23:09.350 line:80%
[Wei Qilin]

00:23:10.830 --> 00:23:15.140 line:80%
and cost 100,000 heroes their lives!

00:23:15.280 --> 00:23:19.150 line:80%
Jinzhou was suffering,
the soldiers seethed.

00:23:19.240 --> 00:23:23.460 line:80%
He caused the Crown Prince's death
and the people to starve to death.

00:23:23.590 --> 00:23:24.110 line:80%
General...

00:23:24.110 --> 00:23:24.840 line:80%
Fan Changyu!

00:23:26.980 --> 00:23:27.780 line:80%
Stop singing!

00:23:28.200 --> 00:23:28.800 line:80%
Come here!

00:23:38.000 --> 00:23:40.200 line:80%
Do you understand why you're kneeling?

00:23:40.830 --> 00:23:41.760 line:80%
Mother,

00:23:41.760 --> 00:23:46.110 line:80%
I won't play
the "Big Traitor" game anymore.

00:23:48.360 --> 00:23:49.490 line:80%
Good girl, Changyu.

00:23:52.630 --> 00:23:53.830 line:80%
How many in this world

00:23:55.410 --> 00:23:56.670 line:80%
can truly distinguish

00:23:57.200 --> 00:24:00.510 line:80%
loyalty from treachery
and right from wrong?

00:24:00.540 --> 00:24:05.130 line:80%
The big traitor, Wei Qilin.

00:24:14.150 --> 00:24:14.990 line:80%
No.

00:24:16.480 --> 00:24:17.680 line:80%
My father was not him.

00:24:21.180 --> 00:24:22.180 line:80%
It's not true.

00:24:23.810 --> 00:24:25.000 line:80%
It's not true!

00:24:25.520 --> 00:24:26.780 line:80%
It's not true!

00:24:32.940 --> 00:24:33.730 line:80%
It's me.

00:24:44.630 --> 00:24:45.360 line:80%
Does it hurt?

00:24:51.070 --> 00:24:52.130 line:80%
Is Sui Yuanqing...

00:24:54.480 --> 00:24:55.310 line:80%
dead?

00:24:58.520 --> 00:24:59.280 line:80%
He escaped.

00:24:59.300 --> 00:25:00.590 line:80%
Your Highness, I've come to save you!

00:25:00.590 --> 00:25:02.390 line:80%
Take the Heir Apparent away now!

00:25:04.310 --> 00:25:04.960 line:80%
Hyah!

00:25:08.200 --> 00:25:08.730 line:80%
Let's go!

00:25:29.110 --> 00:25:30.640 line:80%
He will die sooner or later.

00:25:33.150 --> 00:25:35.780 line:80%
I will bring his head back to Lin'an

00:25:36.000 --> 00:25:37.600 line:80%
to pay tribute to our people.

00:25:41.070 --> 00:25:41.630 line:80%
Alright.

00:25:43.280 --> 00:25:44.410 line:80%
It must hurt, right?

00:25:46.960 --> 00:25:48.160 line:80%
It's just a minor cut.

00:25:51.590 --> 00:25:53.440 line:80%
How is General Wu's injury?

00:25:53.910 --> 00:25:55.310 line:80%
He broke his shoulder.

00:25:55.380 --> 00:25:57.480 line:80%
Fortunately, he's always been strong.

00:25:57.480 --> 00:25:58.880 line:80%
His life is not in danger.

00:25:59.400 --> 00:26:00.400 line:80%
It's just that...

00:26:00.660 --> 00:26:02.860 line:80%
he may not be able to wield a sword again.

00:26:04.610 --> 00:26:06.120 line:80%
It was all to protect me.

00:26:08.970 --> 00:26:11.970 line:80%
He risked his life twice
on the battlefield to save me.

00:26:13.720 --> 00:26:15.240 line:80%
I owe him a lot.

00:26:16.150 --> 00:26:16.960 line:80%
Today,

00:26:17.350 --> 00:26:20.210 line:80%
if he hadn't blocked
that spear from Lord Changxin,

00:26:20.240 --> 00:26:21.400 line:80%
I would have died.

00:26:24.870 --> 00:26:25.760 line:80%
In this world,

00:26:26.850 --> 00:26:28.780 line:80%
No one has the right to make you die.

00:26:36.400 --> 00:26:38.600 line:80%
I've been having nightmares all night.

00:26:39.520 --> 00:26:41.450 line:80%
In them, it was either Mandi's face

00:26:43.390 --> 00:26:45.060 line:80%
or the faces of our soldiers.

00:26:45.590 --> 00:26:48.280 line:80%
They died over and over again
in my dreams.

00:26:51.800 --> 00:26:53.000 line:80%
And every time,

00:26:55.350 --> 00:26:57.440 line:80%
every time, I couldn't save them.

00:27:11.240 --> 00:27:13.590 line:80%
Was the Battle of Jinzhou 17 years ago

00:27:15.280 --> 00:27:16.740 line:80%
just as brutal?

00:27:18.970 --> 00:27:20.170 line:80%
The Battle of Jinzhou

00:27:22.430 --> 00:27:23.580 line:80%
was even worse.

00:27:25.390 --> 00:27:26.590 line:80%
Seventeen years ago,

00:27:27.040 --> 00:27:29.500 line:80%
my father fought the Beijue Army
for months.

00:27:30.200 --> 00:27:31.940 line:80%
But because supplies never arrived

00:27:31.940 --> 00:27:33.550 line:80%
and reinforcements didn't come,

00:27:33.550 --> 00:27:36.590 line:80%
the soldiers were too weak to resist,
and the city fell.

00:27:36.590 --> 00:27:38.590 line:80%
Beijue people marched straight in.

00:27:38.630 --> 00:27:41.240 line:80%
Tens of thousands of lives were treated
as worthless as grass.

00:27:41.240 --> 00:27:44.200 line:80%
And my father was hanged on the city wall.

00:27:51.760 --> 00:27:52.280 line:80%
Then,

00:27:53.480 --> 00:27:56.080 line:80%
the one who transported the grain
back then...

00:27:57.110 --> 00:27:58.030 line:80%
Wei Qilin...

00:27:59.070 --> 00:28:00.070 line:80%
Did he really...

00:28:02.390 --> 00:28:03.920 line:80%
cause so many people to die?

00:28:06.720 --> 00:28:09.200 line:80%
Is it possible there's another story?

00:28:10.450 --> 00:28:11.450 line:80%
Wei Qilin

00:28:12.330 --> 00:28:15.440 line:80%
was Wei Yan's
most trusted general back then.

00:28:16.760 --> 00:28:19.090 line:80%
He also fought side by side
with my father.

00:28:19.760 --> 00:28:21.560 line:80%
He was a loyal and righteous man.

00:28:21.590 --> 00:28:22.630 line:80%
But later,

00:28:25.070 --> 00:28:26.870 line:80%
in the eyes of the Yanzhou Army,

00:28:27.480 --> 00:28:29.280 line:80%
he became a traitor to Great Yin.

00:28:32.590 --> 00:28:34.960 line:80%
Why do you suddenly ask about this?

00:28:36.240 --> 00:28:38.910 line:80%
Fan Changyu, tell him.

00:28:40.110 --> 00:28:42.640 line:80%
Telling him the truth
is the right thing to do.

00:28:43.800 --> 00:28:45.630 line:80%
Even if he turns against you from now on,

00:28:45.630 --> 00:28:47.690 line:80%
it would just be the right thing to do.

00:28:47.720 --> 00:28:48.550 line:80%
Tell him!

00:28:49.520 --> 00:28:50.310 line:80%
Changyu?

00:28:52.150 --> 00:28:52.960 line:80%
I want to know,

00:28:55.870 --> 00:28:58.280 line:80%
when will General He's funeral be held?

00:29:01.390 --> 00:29:02.350 line:80%
In 6 days.

00:29:03.070 --> 00:29:07.730 line:80%
General He's seventh-day memorial
coincides with my father's memorial ceremony.

00:29:09.840 --> 00:29:13.050 line:80%
It's almost like it was destined.

00:29:14.440 --> 00:29:15.970 line:80%
Seventeen years ago today,

00:29:16.870 --> 00:29:18.870 line:80%
my father died in battle in Jinzhou.

00:29:19.310 --> 00:29:20.640 line:80%
Every year at this time,

00:29:20.760 --> 00:29:22.490 line:80%
the generals of the Xie family,

00:29:23.350 --> 00:29:24.750 line:80%
no matter where they are,

00:29:25.260 --> 00:29:27.590 line:80%
return to pay their respects to my father.

00:29:28.000 --> 00:29:29.110 line:80%
Then at that time,

00:29:30.680 --> 00:29:33.140 line:80%
I also want to offer incense
for General Xie.

00:29:33.520 --> 00:29:34.350 line:80%
May I?

00:29:37.040 --> 00:29:37.520 line:80%
Yes.

00:29:45.820 --> 00:29:49.910 line:80%
[The Coffin of He Jingyuan,
General of Loyalty of Great Yin]

00:29:53.860 --> 00:29:56.070 line:80%
[In Memory of My Late Father, Xie Linshan]

00:29:55.350 --> 00:29:56.200 line:80%
Wenkan,

00:29:56.910 --> 00:29:58.720 line:80%
since you were a child,

00:29:59.150 --> 00:30:00.830 line:80%
you've been following me.

00:30:01.350 --> 00:30:04.070 line:80%
You are my proudest student.

00:30:05.440 --> 00:30:08.550 line:80%
The reason I kept you by my side

00:30:08.870 --> 00:30:12.200 line:80%
is that the court
is treacherous and unpredictable.

00:30:12.220 --> 00:30:14.550 line:80%
The Li and Wei factions manipulate power.

00:30:15.760 --> 00:30:18.040 line:80%
I don't want you to be misled by them

00:30:18.310 --> 00:30:21.240 line:80%
and become a pawn in their schemes.

00:30:22.800 --> 00:30:24.200 line:80%
What I hope for

00:30:24.870 --> 00:30:27.470 line:80%
is that you become a loyal subject
of Great Yin.

00:30:31.830 --> 00:30:33.160 line:80%
There is one more thing.

00:30:33.240 --> 00:30:34.840 line:80%
It concerns the Fan sisters.

00:30:35.590 --> 00:30:37.020 line:80%
After I am gone,

00:30:37.630 --> 00:30:40.480 line:80%
I hope you can treat them with sincerity.

00:30:41.000 --> 00:30:46.440 line:80%
Only then can I rest in peace.

00:30:51.240 --> 00:30:54.770 line:80%
Lord Li, this is the elegiac couplet
sent by Prime Minister Wei.

00:30:55.490 --> 00:30:58.050 line:80%
[With iron will and a tempered blade,
he chilled the enemy;]

00:30:57.970 --> 00:30:58.720 line:80%
Lord Li,

00:30:58.050 --> 00:31:00.620 line:80%
[his loyal name shines like the sun,
his spirit stands tall.]

00:30:59.560 --> 00:31:02.360 line:80%
this is the elegiac couplet
sent by Grand Tutor Li.

00:31:02.640 --> 00:31:05.190 line:80%
His blood-forged soul shines in history;
his righteous courage humbles us.

00:31:06.310 --> 00:31:08.830 line:80%
My Lord, which pair
have you decided to hang?

00:31:24.540 --> 00:31:28.670 line:80%
This means you've decided to help
the Grand Tutor against the Wei faction?

00:31:49.390 --> 00:31:52.200 line:80%
I, Huaian, will carry on your legacy,

00:31:53.310 --> 00:31:54.350 line:80%
and won't let down
the soldiers and civilians

00:31:54.350 --> 00:31:56.610 line:80%
of Great Yin who sacrificed their lives.

00:32:11.040 --> 00:32:16.690 line:80%
[Ximo Pavilion]

00:32:36.830 --> 00:32:37.590 line:80%
Cousin.

00:32:38.240 --> 00:32:39.040 line:80%
Please enjoy.

00:32:45.730 --> 00:32:48.920 line:80%
[Liu Wan'er, the illegitimate daughter
of a cousin of Lord Changxin's wife]

00:32:52.350 --> 00:32:53.240 line:80%
Mother said...

00:32:54.280 --> 00:32:56.720 line:80%
your injuries are severe.

00:32:57.550 --> 00:32:59.000 line:80%
This tonic is good for...

00:32:59.910 --> 00:33:01.870 line:80%
healing wounds.

00:33:02.360 --> 00:33:03.290 line:80%
She also said...

00:33:03.840 --> 00:33:05.700 line:80%
that Father has already found out

00:33:06.070 --> 00:33:08.520 line:80%
the Marquis of Wu'an
isn't paying attention to this place.

00:33:08.520 --> 00:33:09.850 line:80%
So please, stay here...

00:33:11.550 --> 00:33:12.750 line:80%
and recover in peace.

00:33:20.340 --> 00:33:22.200 line:80%
Why are you shaking so badly?

00:33:23.050 --> 00:33:24.180 line:80%
Are you afraid of me?

00:33:43.040 --> 00:33:43.910 line:80%
Cousin!

00:33:48.350 --> 00:33:49.440 line:80%
Careful. It's hot.

00:33:55.870 --> 00:33:57.310 line:80%
I don't like plain food.

00:33:58.140 --> 00:33:59.350 line:80%
Why don't you...

00:33:59.960 --> 00:34:01.220 line:80%
drink it for me?

00:34:03.040 --> 00:34:03.520 line:80%
I...

00:34:09.160 --> 00:34:10.019 line:80%
Cousin!

00:34:10.959 --> 00:34:12.229 line:80%
Run.

00:34:13.120 --> 00:34:16.390 line:80%
Father heard that the Marquis of Wu'an
is coming to arrest you personally

00:34:16.390 --> 00:34:19.650 line:80%
and is afraid that our whole family
will be executed if the city falls.

00:34:19.650 --> 00:34:21.370 line:80%
He put poison in the soup,

00:34:21.880 --> 00:34:24.410 line:80%
saying he would offer your head
to surrender.

00:34:24.470 --> 00:34:25.310 line:80%
I'm so sorry.

00:34:26.430 --> 00:34:27.830 line:80%
I didn't want to hurt you.

00:34:31.860 --> 00:34:33.990 line:80%
Thanks for telling me, Cousin.

00:34:50.740 --> 00:34:55.470 line:80%
[Ximo Pavilion]

00:35:05.420 --> 00:35:06.030 line:80%
Father!

00:35:06.760 --> 00:35:07.380 line:80%
Father!

00:35:07.740 --> 00:35:08.380 line:80%
Mother!

00:35:09.470 --> 00:35:10.310 line:80%
Mother!

00:35:10.870 --> 00:35:13.660 line:80%
Why did you kill my parents?

00:35:14.120 --> 00:35:15.430 line:80%
With your skills,

00:35:15.520 --> 00:35:17.510 line:80%
you could have escaped!

00:35:17.760 --> 00:35:20.100 line:80%
Why didn't you just run?

00:35:20.200 --> 00:35:22.800 line:80%
Why did you have to kill them?

00:35:23.280 --> 00:35:25.810 line:80%
They were going to offer my head
to surrender.

00:35:26.340 --> 00:35:27.820 line:80%
Why couldn't I kill them?

00:35:34.720 --> 00:35:36.380 line:80%
They aren't worth your tears.

00:35:37.460 --> 00:35:39.400 line:80%
You don't mean that much to them.

00:35:40.800 --> 00:35:41.640 line:80%
Otherwise,

00:35:42.050 --> 00:35:45.310 line:80%
they wouldn't have sent you
to bring me that poisoned soup.

00:35:46.560 --> 00:35:47.390 line:80%
Now,

00:35:48.910 --> 00:35:49.830 line:80%
you are free.

00:36:15.880 --> 00:36:18.520 line:80%
Cousin, take me with you.

00:36:18.560 --> 00:36:20.080 line:80%
My family is dead.

00:36:20.080 --> 00:36:22.600 line:80%
I don't know where to go.

00:36:24.760 --> 00:36:26.440 line:80%
I killed your whole family,

00:36:26.870 --> 00:36:28.600 line:80%
and you still want to follow me?

00:36:28.900 --> 00:36:30.250 line:80%
I'm begging you.

00:36:30.680 --> 00:36:32.550 line:80%
Please take me with you.

00:36:38.350 --> 00:36:40.390 line:80%
What a delicate flower.

00:36:42.050 --> 00:36:44.230 line:80%
But why are some flowers, like you,

00:36:44.680 --> 00:36:47.010 line:80%
only able to cling to
and depend on others?

00:36:47.610 --> 00:36:48.730 line:80%
Without others,

00:36:49.350 --> 00:36:51.080 line:80%
you can't survive for a moment.

00:36:52.300 --> 00:36:53.700 line:80%
And some flowers

00:36:54.110 --> 00:36:55.900 line:80%
grow wild and free,

00:36:57.240 --> 00:36:58.970 line:80%
are covered in thorns,

00:36:59.510 --> 00:37:02.850 line:80%
and make you love and hate them
at the same time.

00:38:36.240 --> 00:38:40.300 line:80%
Master, the Heir Apparent slaughtered
the entire Liu family last night.

00:38:41.680 --> 00:38:42.720 line:80%
Big deal.

00:38:43.270 --> 00:38:45.270 line:80%
It's nothing to be surprised about.

00:38:45.870 --> 00:38:46.600 line:80%
Where is he?

00:38:47.160 --> 00:38:47.910 line:80%
In the study.

00:38:51.310 --> 00:38:52.030 line:80%
Yuanqing!

00:38:53.470 --> 00:38:54.160 line:80%
Yuanqing!

00:38:54.830 --> 00:38:55.470 line:80%
Min!

00:38:55.990 --> 00:38:57.320 line:80%
I've finally found you.

00:38:58.990 --> 00:38:59.870 line:80%
How are you?

00:39:00.360 --> 00:39:01.420 line:80%
Is Mother alright?

00:39:05.870 --> 00:39:06.620 line:80%
Min,

00:39:08.200 --> 00:39:09.470 line:80%
am I really...

00:39:10.470 --> 00:39:12.130 line:80%
really inferior to Xie Zheng?

00:39:12.800 --> 00:39:14.240 line:80%
Is that why I keep losing

00:39:14.870 --> 00:39:16.400 line:80%
and caused Father's death?

00:39:19.020 --> 00:39:20.060 line:80%
To me,

00:39:20.760 --> 00:39:23.870 line:80%
you are the most formidable man
in this world.

00:39:25.030 --> 00:39:27.830 line:80%
Xie Zheng only won
a few battles by sheer luck.

00:39:28.490 --> 00:39:30.220 line:80%
But our great cause is not lost.

00:39:30.540 --> 00:39:31.820 line:80%
We still have a chance.

00:39:33.030 --> 00:39:33.960 line:80%
Our great cause?

00:39:36.310 --> 00:39:37.970 line:80%
It's nothing but an illusion.

00:39:38.800 --> 00:39:41.350 line:80%
Ever since Father
was misled by the Late Emperor,

00:39:41.350 --> 00:39:43.120 line:80%
he was obsessed with achieving
this so-called great cause.

00:39:43.120 --> 00:39:44.080 line:80%
And in the end?

00:39:44.350 --> 00:39:45.610 line:80%
It was all for nothing.

00:39:46.640 --> 00:39:48.750 line:80%
I don't believe in this bullshit cause.

00:39:48.750 --> 00:39:50.880 line:80%
What do I care who becomes the Emperor?

00:39:53.270 --> 00:39:54.240 line:80%
The Sui family

00:39:54.950 --> 00:39:56.350 line:80%
cannot give up so easily!

00:39:56.660 --> 00:39:59.930 line:80%
Just because Xie Zheng
has every advantage,

00:40:00.510 --> 00:40:02.280 line:80%
you're afraid to seek revenge?

00:40:03.160 --> 00:40:04.890 line:80%
Even though I am in poor health,

00:40:05.310 --> 00:40:07.390 line:80%
I will use every last bit of strength
in this broken body

00:40:07.390 --> 00:40:08.990 line:80%
to fight them to the death!

00:40:09.240 --> 00:40:10.120 line:80%
What about you?

00:40:10.560 --> 00:40:12.910 line:80%
A true man stands tall
between Heaven and Earth.

00:40:12.910 --> 00:40:15.240 line:80%
How can you accept defeat without a fight?

00:40:15.390 --> 00:40:16.570 line:80%
If we cannot win,

00:40:17.080 --> 00:40:18.200 line:80%
that is our fate!

00:40:20.720 --> 00:40:21.720 line:80%
Look at you today.

00:40:22.200 --> 00:40:23.680 line:80%
You're a complete mess!

00:40:23.680 --> 00:40:26.080 line:80%
How can you face
Father's spirit in Heaven?

00:40:26.600 --> 00:40:29.870 line:80%
Do you know who killed Father?

00:40:31.840 --> 00:40:33.000 line:80%
It wasn't Xie Zheng?

00:40:33.390 --> 00:40:35.810 line:80%
It was Fan Changyu.

00:40:39.990 --> 00:40:41.280 line:80%
Fan Changyu?

00:40:44.240 --> 00:40:45.440 line:80%
Fan Changyu!

00:40:46.470 --> 00:40:47.520 line:80%
She again?

00:40:47.830 --> 00:40:49.540 line:80%
That butcher girl again?

00:40:49.640 --> 00:40:51.280 line:80%
How dare she!

00:40:53.800 --> 00:40:54.350 line:80%
Min!

00:40:54.870 --> 00:40:56.030 line:80%
I want revenge!

00:40:59.080 --> 00:40:59.950 line:80%
Go ahead.

00:41:00.280 --> 00:41:01.470 line:80%
No matter what you do,

00:41:01.470 --> 00:41:02.530 line:80%
I will support you.

00:41:03.240 --> 00:41:04.680 line:80%
I will take care of Mother along the way.

00:41:04.680 --> 00:41:06.350 line:80%
Just go and kill Fan Changyu

00:41:06.640 --> 00:41:08.430 line:80%
to appease Father's spirit in Heaven.